### Test the auth package with these requests
### (Use REST Client extension in VS Code)

@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000

### 1. Login to get a token
POST {{baseUrl}}/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "testuser"
}

### 2. Access protected route (replace YOUR_TOKEN with token from step 1)
GET {{baseUrl}}/protected
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN

### 3. Get profile (replace YOUR_TOKEN with token from step 1)
GET {{baseUrl}}/profile
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN

### 4. Test without token (should fail)
GET {{baseUrl}}/protected

### 5. Test with invalid token (should fail)
GET {{baseUrl}}/protected
Authorization: Bearer invalid.token.here
